entity.name: Hundreds of protesters fill a Moscow square for day three of election protests
entity.description: For the third consecutive day, protesters gathered in Moscow to demand fair city parliament elections. Authorities have barred 27 candidates, including @IlyaYashin, so far from registering. Yulia @Galiamina, one of the disqualified candidates, has called upon attendees to continue protesting.
